<div class="alert alert-success">
[% IF project.archived;
    IF can_unarchive %]
    <form id="unarchive" method="post" action="[% project_urls.unarchive %]"></form>
    <p class="m-0">
        üìÅ This project is archived (read-only). You can
        <button class="alert-link" type="submit" form="unarchive">Un-archive this project</button>
    </p>
    [% ELSE %]
    <p class="m-0">üìÅ This project has been archived.</p>
    [% END;
ELSIF can_edit %]
    <p class="m-0">
    [% IF inventory.quantities == 0
        AND inventory.articles == 0
        AND inventory.meals == 0
        AND inventory.shop_sections == 0
        AND inventory.tags == 0 %]
        This is a fresh project without any data.
        You can <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.import %]">import data</a> from other projects
        or start from scratch, e.g. by <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.quantities %]">creating quantities</a>.
    [% ELSIF inventory.quantities == 0 %]
        This project lacks any quantities. You can <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.import %]">import them</a>
        or <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.quantities %]">create some</a> from scratch.
    [% ELSIF inventory.units == 0 %]
        This project lacks any units. You can <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.units %]">create some</a>.
    [% ELSIF inventory.articles == 0 %]
        This project lacks any articles. You can <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.import %]">import them</a>
        or <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.articles %]">create some</a> from scratch.
    [% ELSIF inventory.meals == 0 OR inventory.dishes == 0 %]
        This project lacks any [% inventory.meals == 0 ? 'meals' : 'dishes' %].
        You can <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.edit %]">create some</a> now.
        [% IF inventory.recipes == 0 %]
            You can also <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.recipes %]">create a recipe</a> for dishes.
        [% END %]
    [% ELSIF inventory.purchase_lists == 0 %]
        This project lacks any purchase lists. You can <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.purchase_lists %]">create some</a>.
    [% ELSIF inventory.unassigned_items > 0 %]
        There are some ingredient items not yet assigned to a purchase list.
        You can <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.unassigned_items %]">assign items to purchase lists</a> now.
    [% ELSIF project.is_stale %]
        <form class="d-inline" method="post" action="[% project_urls.archive %]">
            This project is stale (all meals and purchase lists in are in the past).
            You can <button class="alert-link" type="submit">üìÅ Archive this project</button>
        </form>
    [% ELSE %]
        Once you‚Äôve finished this project you can <a class="alert-link" href="[% project_urls.print %]">print documents</a> to take action.
    [% END;
END %]
</div>

[% INCLUDE 'print/project.tt' %]

<p>Created at [% display_datetime(project.created) %] UTC</p>
